# Unicode.GeneralCategory.finalPunctuation

**Case**

A final quotation mark.

## Declaration

```swift
case finalPunctuation
```

## Discussion

This value corresponds to the category `Final_Punctuation` (abbreviated `Pf`) in the [https://unicode.org/reports/tr44/#General_Category_Values].
